ntura Blvd., Suite 2230, Sherman Oaks, CA 91403 USA</span></li></ul><p> </p><h2><a id="_Purposes_and_legal_1"></a>Purposes and legal basis for the processing</h2><p>Xsolla processes personal data for the following purposes and on the following legal basis:</p><table><thead><tr><th><p><strong>Purpose</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Legal Basis</strong></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>To license different software (including computer games) for a fee to the users of the website.</p></td><td><p>Performance of a contract to which the data subject is party.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>To provide smooth functioning of the website by storing users’ information (so that they do not have to reenter it during their current or future website sessions) and with the use of third parties’ hosting, maintenance, and security services.</p></td><td><p>Performance of a contract to which the data subject is party.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>To improve design and functions of the website on the basis of analysis of users’ behavior on the website and aggregate website usage metrics (total number of visitors and pages accessed).</p></td><td><p>Legitimate interests pursued by Xsolla.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>To automatically update the software purchased by the users of the website from Xsolla.</p></td><td><p>Performance of a contract to which the data subject is party.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>To provide the users of the website (at their request) with information on the terms of their probable cooperation with Xsolla or the capabilities of services offered by Xsolla.</p></td><td><p>Necessity of the processing in order to take steps at the request of the data subject prior to entering into a contract.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>For conventional direct marketing and other forms of marketing or advertisement.</p></td><td><p>Legitimate interests pursued by Xsolla.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>For enforcement of legal claims including debt collection via out-of-court procedures; prevention of fraud or 