ated_decision-making"></a><a id="_Automated_decision-making_including"></a>Automated decision-making including profiling</h2><p>Xsolla analyzes personal data of the users of the website to predict their future requests and to provide them with individual proposals.<br /></p><h2><a id="_Children’s_Privacy"></a>Children’s Privacy</h2><p>Xsolla does not process personal data of children under 13 and takes appropriate measures to ensure that they do not use its services. If you find out that a child under 13 has provided Xsolla with his or her personal data, please contact Xsolla at <a href="mailto:support@xsolla.com">support@xsolla.com</a>.</p><p><a id="_Data_Security"></a></p><h2><a id="_Your_California_Privacy"></a>California Privacy Rights</h2><p>Under Section 1798.83 of California Civil Code, data subjects that are California residents can ask Xsolla to provide information on disclosure of their personal data to third parties for direct marketing purposes of these third parties. To make such a request, California residents can contact Xsolla via the following email <a href="mailto:support@xsolla.com">support@xsolla.com</a>.</p><h2><a id="_Changes_to_this"></a>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2><p>Xsolla may change this Privacy Policy from time to time at its sole discretion. If so, Xsolla notifies the users of the websites about these changes by a pop-up line on the website.</p><ol class="footnotes"><li id="footnote-1"><p> Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data, and repealing Directive 95/46/EC. <a href="#footnote-ref-1">↑</a></p></span></li></ol>',"http.0":"API 要求參數錯誤","http.001-001":"使用者取消認證","http.002-040":"使用者已遭禁","http.003-001":"使用者名稱或密碼錯誤","http.003-002":"未找到使用者","http.003-003":"使用者名稱已存在","http.003-004":"此電子郵件已註冊","http.003-005":"電子郵件不存在","http.003-007":"使用者未啟用（電子郵件未確認）","http.003-008":"不得更改